Greetings and Salutations,

The operation that you are using here:

exp(alpha1(0)+beta1(1));

Returns a double instead of an arma::vec. Hence,

from ?double? to ?arma::vec {aka arma::Col<double>}?

To fix this, use:

        arma::vec temp(1);
        temp << exp(alpha1(0)+beta1(1)); // assumes 1 element in alpha1 and 2 elements in beta1
        return temp;

In addition, you should supply a return at the end of the function?

  return arma::zeros<arma::vec>(0);

Returns a vector of length 0.

Sincerely,

JJB

